你能够调用以下的API:
[['ResearchPaperSearch.find_papers', {'name': 'ResearchPaperSearch.find_papers', 'description': 'This function searches for research papers based on topic and year.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'topic', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The topic of the research paper, e.g., AI in banking.'}, {'name': 'year', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'The year of publication.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'papers', 'description': 'A list of up to three matching research papers, each with a title, authors, and abstract.'}]}], ['ReportRetrieval.get_report', {'name': 'ReportRetrieval.get_report', 'description': 'This function retrieves a specific report given the bank name and date.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'bankName', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The name of the bank.'}, {'name': 'date', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The date of the report in YYYY-MM-DD format.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'report', 'description': 'The detailed report content.'}]}], ['FinancialData.get_real_time_data', {'name': 'FinancialData.get_real_time_data', 'description': 'This function retrieves real-time financial data for a specific bank.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'bankName', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The name of the bank.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'financialData', 'description': 'Real-time financial data including stock prices, revenue, and profit.'}]}], ['AIProjectDetails.get_details', {'name': 'AIProjectDetails.get_details', 'description': 'This function retrieves detailed information about AI projects of a specific bank.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'bankName', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The name of the bank.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'projectDetails', 'description': 'Detailed information about the AI projects, including objectives, technologies used, and outcomes.'}]}], ['TechDevelopment.get_suggestions', {'name': 'TechDevelopment.get_suggestions', 'description': 'This function provides technical development suggestions for AI projects of a specific bank.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'bankName', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The name of the bank.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'suggestions', 'description': 'Technical development suggestions for improving AI projects.'}]}]]
请生成一个解决用户问题的计划，计划应该是一个行为列表，每个行为的格式如下:

[{
    // 动作的ID
    "id": number;
    // 动作要调用的API名称
    "name": string;
    // 当前API的参数输入(JSON格式)
    "args": "str(Record<string, any>)";
}, ...
]

你可以在计划中想象参数的值，这些指令将按顺序执行。
例如，如果你想调用 `ResearchPaperSearch.find_papers` 并传入 `topic` 和 `year`，你可以写下面的计划:

[{
    "id": 0,
    "name": "ResearchPaperSearch.find_papers",
    "args": "{'topic': 'AI in banking', 'year': 2024}",
}, ...
]

这些参数将在执行时被替换为真实的值。请注意，参数应该是一个字符串，而不是一个字典。
请在字典的参数中使用 ''，在其他地方使用 ""，不要打印值为 None 或 null 的参数。

你应该只生成一个 JSON 格式的计划列表。列表应该是完整的计划列表，不要有 `...`。
不要生成任何解释 JSON 的文本。
